Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That which blooms when everyone \Ngrows silent is a false spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you stay too long to enjoy the spring, before long, your body grows icy cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Blossoms...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:28.62,EP Title BG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,0)\p1\blur1}m 0 0 l 950 0 950 100 0 100
