Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:02:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.26,0:03:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I got caught in this snow. \NCould you put me up for the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Miharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could he be wandering off\N to so early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's dangerous! Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:04:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Miharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to tell him to keep his hands off of strange things he finds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was an unusual one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're at it again?! Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me... You can see what he sees, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We call them mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who can see them are either afraid of them or fascinated by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy definitely seems to be the latter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he's always liked living creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He would catch them and bring them home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since he began seeing those \Nthings three winters ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:04:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,he's been behaving strangely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That winter, Miharu went missing \Nafter he went into the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,For several days after that, there was a blizzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back. There's nothing more we can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought there wasn't any hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.26,0:05:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.61,0:05:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Miharu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He returned unexpectedly when the spring came.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, he began saying that he sees strange things and chasing after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1937)}Then, when our winter food stores were just about gone, he'd suddenly disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Later that night, we'd find him collapsed on the outskirts of the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and he'd stay in a deep sleep until spring came.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:06:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In his pocket, he'd have mountain \Ngreens that never grew in winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When I asked him where he'd been, he'd say...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't open the bag outside the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be trouble if everyone found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That was all he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We've only got each other so I can \Nunderstand he's trying to help out, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it, it isn't normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... {\i1}Harumagai{\i0} might be the cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haru... magai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard there's a mushi called {\i1}usobuki{\i0} that looks like tree blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They have a peculiar scent that makes hibernating animals and plants active.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they suck out the life energy of those animals that they lured out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The animals whose energy was sucked outfall back into sleep until spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:07:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything more than that, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly are mushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not all of them are frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you don't mess with them, \Nthey're not much of a problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but in your brother's case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, I could teach him \Nwhich ones are dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miharu, see that one over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.89,0:07:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That one is a troublemaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, pay attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! You can find lots of them in these places!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh... Don't pull them out... Can't you stay still...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darn... I should've thought before agreeing to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, where do you find those mountain greens?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm planning to take them from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, show me the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're planning to tell my sister, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want to do is study them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize you're making your sister worry, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,At least tell her where this place is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do, she'll follow me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you want to help her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,if you ignore her concern for you, \Nyou're just being selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You've a place where you belong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go stepping too far into the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've seen this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then how about these?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... never seen them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Miharu! Pay attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, Ginko-san, can we continue this tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine with me... I don't have much else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how long can you stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Not sure. It depends on the area...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think I can stay until he at least \Nlearns the mushi in this locale.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.86,0:09:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a quick learner,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,so... maybe about another ten days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on the area?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.47,0:09:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I seem to be a mushi magnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stay long in rich soil areas\N where many mushi live...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing good will come from \Ntoo many mushi in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But judging from the mushi that Miharu's seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't seem that this area has rich soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There'd probably be no harm in staying here a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.13,0:09:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're welcome to stay as long as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Traveling in winter is difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.31,0:09:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay until spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... that depends on the mountain conditions...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A chrysalis?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.56,0:10:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think it was around there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.57,0:10:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It looked like... a mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have I begun to attract them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm right. There are more than there were before...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I've stayed a bit too long...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ginko! I have business in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Look after Miharu for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's inside, sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miharu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn that kid... he's gone wandering off again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How far did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn... which way did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Miharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should go back and start again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Miharu! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Harumagai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Suzu... Don't be so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,His symptoms are the same as usual, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll awaken in the spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to stay with you until then,\N but I have to be on my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But Miharu will miss you when he awakens...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come back to see you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everyone awakens, the false ones go to sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And when winter comes once again to the mountains, they pretend it's spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Suzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Gin...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been asleep for a year?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.84,0:14:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I just don't know what went wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll just have to find where Miharu used to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But you might end up like Miharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Miharu was supposed to awaken in the spring, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it's that woke him up is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If I go there, I should be able to find out what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't make it back, search the mountain's north side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Last year, Miharu's footprints headed in this direction...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the same kind that was in Miharu's bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A sweet scent...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel giddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd better get out of here quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I recall usobuki take the form of tree blossoms...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They all look like ordinary blossoms...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where is the clue I'm looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.01,0:16:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Its body temperature is dropping rapidly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.31,0:16:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The scent has changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My body's getting colder all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't... move my hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are only those butterflies still?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I know... but I'm so... sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do to wake them up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed like... something flew out...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this scent?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh... spring is already here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Miharu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Miharu! Miha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, the flower-like object on the ceiling released a strong scent
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,for a few days and then transformed into something I've seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't imagine that chrysalis like \Nobject I saw then was a {\i1}usobuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you used the {\i1}usobuki's{\i0} emergence as a signal for the {\i1}harumagai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... If you hadn't let the butterfly escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it would've become a flower \Nin spring and awakened me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've told me that sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked those butterflies the most, so I wanted to keep them a secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.57,0:20:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They grow mountain greens in the\N winter, which helps us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're so beautiful flying around in the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:21:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're just doing it to gather\N food to survive, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well well... You're beginning to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, they're certainly not our friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.46,0:21:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just unusual neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're free to like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, why don't you drop by the house before you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I've stayed too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I should leave as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis will feel sad if you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.16,0:21:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell her thank you for all she has done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.17,0:21:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You'll come again, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.07,0:22:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? Well, not in winter, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.14,0:22:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.94,0:22:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,People grow weak during the winter too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.14,0:22:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An illusionary spring where buds \Nblossom in the icy mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The light from homes that illuminates the snowy path...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.83,0:22:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They are tempting and invite for a prolonged stay...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.22,0:22:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Animals and mushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1854)\i1}and humans as well...
